title: Amy Acker @ Northern FanCon  2019
author: AmyAckerFanGuyChannel
comment: This was taken from another channel.  You should at least credit who originally created it.

Where was this at??   Amy looks so sweet and beautiful!!   Amy is such a charmer.  She is without a doubt the best looking woman on television or in the movies!  Amy Acker is in a league of her own!!   Who agrees with me on this??
OMG, I cannot hear myself think.

Starting at around 2:41, the guy needs to be corrected, there were only FIVE seasons of Person of Interest, not seven or eight.  Like many others have said, I believe the show was canceled prematurely, but it is what it is, and at least we got to see Amy in about 65 episodes over the few years it was on.
description: Location: Prince George, British Columbia, Canada
